# Xylogics 753 or 7053 VME SMD disk controllers and disks, found
# on sun4 systems.
#xdc0	at vmel0 addr 0xffffee80 level 3 vect 0x44
#xdc1	at vmel0 addr 0xffffee90 level 3 vect 0x45
